elements.name: Verify the PromoTile, add products to trolley and verify the status of the product in PromoTile for guest user

steps.name: user continue to connect to apigee with login username as "SHOPPER_USERNAME10"
connection from user to apigee endpoint happens
I search for the address "Darcy Road"
I select the "1" address as fulfilment address from matching addresses
I make a request to Homepage in "online" mode with "NoEDR" and verify the response with PromoCard
I navigate to PromoTile from Homepage in "online" mode
I add the stockcode with quantity "3" to trolley
I verify the stockcode is set to "3" when I make a request to PromoTile
I clear the trolley
I verify the stockcode is not added to trolley when I make a request to PromoTile
